{"tid":1203523,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"俾龜𢭃 講英文","createTime":"2019-06-11T12:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:37:24.000Z","uid":188640,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2be01f3e392610ca84487940ebc81c11f09f42d2","tid":1203523,"uid":188640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">香港特別行政區的行政機關、立法機關和司法機關，除使用中文外，還可使用英文，英文也是正式語文。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n同啲毅進仔練吓香港法定語言英文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲狗一吠就同佢講 May I beg pardon?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多啲英文自己都有得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08698b788f874477fc6f18a174b4afa57faca0f5","tid":1203523,"uid":201823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"毅進仔痛處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79194c940bc0f2d1e47288f5d2c0d2adb8880e13","tid":1203523,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"Dog Barking At Me"},{"pid":"99b24bd75aca8021202812bdb6196739adc98bd9","tid":1203523,"uid":2383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"要佢用英文同你解釋點解搜身"},{"pid":"0ac3fffb689687a23a776d11294dce20e11f0ca7","tid":1203523,"uid":188640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"Searching<br />\n<br />\nIf a police officer finds any person whom he reasonably suspects of having committed or of being about to commit or of intending to commit any offence, he can search him/her for anything that is likely to be of value to the investigation of any offence that the person has committed, or is reasonably suspected of having committed or of being about to commit or of intending to commit.<br />\n<br />\nWithout prejudicing operational efficiency, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">a police officer will inform a person of the reason for a search </span></strong>and the intended scope of the search, prior to conducting a search.<br />\n<br />\nRetrieved from <a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_en/11_useful_info/power_ssa.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_en%2F11_useful_info%2Fpower_ssa.html&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=04e41711\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_en/11_useful_info/power_ssa.html</a>"},{"pid":"2203d15aa948de0f00f6d6234f9b2a0126daf61c","tid":1203523,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"試過有朋友有次三個人係架車到被人截停查<br />\n一個外國讀完書 一個空少一個做老闆 剩係講英文啲差人都無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08eb86176e93a19627dc1a37f812e9f1605f7c79","tid":1203523,"uid":188640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2203d15aa948de0f00f6d6234f9b2a0126daf61c","tid":1203523,"uid":108756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"試過有朋友有次三個人係架車到被人截停查<br />\n一個外國讀完書 一個空少一個做老闆 剩係講英文啲差人都無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"上次返香港俾龜𢭃我都係講英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}